/>\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 就日皇明仁去年向國民暗示退位的意願，日本專家會議公佈指退位只限於日皇明仁一人的方案為最佳方案。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170124/00180_019.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170124%2F00180_019.html&d=qxVWWVIkSK%2BieYma0ob7LksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=fabe3b06\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170124/00180_019.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 哥倫比亞再次舉行一度被禁的鬥牛活動，不少人不滿法院推翻禁令而前往活動場地示威抗議，並與觀眾及警員爆發衝突，最終有多人被捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170124/00180_021.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170124%2F00180_021.html&d=qxVWWVIkSK%2BieYma0ob7LksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=9197a386\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170124/00180_021.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 西班牙宣佈，經過歐洲多國及國際刑警組織等的調查，一個跨國走私藝術品的集團被搗破，並拘捕合共75人，起獲3500件被盜去的古董藝術品。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170124/00180_023.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170124%2F00180_023.html&d=qxVWWVIkSK%2BieYma0ob7LksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=92dcf0ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170124/00180_023.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 美國的密西西比、阿拉巴馬、佛羅里達和喬治亞州遭強勁風暴及龍捲風吹襲，造成最少18人死亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170124/s00014/1485194472501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170124%2Fs00014%2F1485194472501&d=qxVWWVIkSK%2BieYma0ob7LksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=86e2b5b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%